A MAN has been arrested in connection with an alleged sexual assault.

The incident involving a 29-year-old woman happened between 10.30pm and 11pm in Clarkston, East Renfrewshire, on October 18.
Police Scotland said a 47-year-old man has been arrested and is detained in police custody.
He is expected to appear at Paisley Sheriff Court tomorrow.
 